{"data":[{"date":"07:04 18/07","title":"\u201cBrazil c\u1ee7a Tite v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/brazil-cua-tite-vao-tu-ket-world-cup-da-la-gioi-lam-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft WC 2018</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018, \u0110T Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i ba bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00e0u l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e0 Neymar, Selecao t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fap v\u00e0ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 6.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Brazil v\u1eabn su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd v\u1ea5p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t \u0110T B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i cay \u0111\u1eafng d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/buffon-that-bai-tai-world-cup-2018-se-giup-neymar-manh-me-hon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Brazil c\u1ee7a Neymar d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Renato Augusto khi v\u00e0o thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 Brazil l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Samba bao g\u1ed3m 1 b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Fernandinho, 1 t\u1eeb c\u00fa s\u00fat xa tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Kevin De Bruyne.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kaka l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 Brazil c\u1ee7a Tite</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kaka kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi \u0110T Brazil, kh\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World cup c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Nh\u01b0ng x\u00e9t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, ng\u00f4i sao l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Real Madrid v\u00e0 AC Milan tin r\u1eb1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Selecao v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7y t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite\" title=\"HLV Tite\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Brazil-bi-loai-khoi-World-Cup-Tite-dang-trach-1,-Neymar-dang-trach-10-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin \u1edf HLV Tite</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>T\u1ea1i Brazil, lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</em>&rdquo;, Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Omnisport. &ldquo;<em>Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i th\u00edch nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>G\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. Hai HLV \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 cho ch\u00fang ta nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng may m\u1eafn. C\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Thiago Silva ch\u1ea1m c\u1ed9t v\u00e0 \u0111i ra ngo\u00e0i. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Kompany ch\u1ea1m Fernandinho v\u00e0 \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</em>&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;<em>Brazil c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfm khuy\u1ebft, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa. N\u1ebfu Tite ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i ch\u00fang t\u1eeb gi\u1edd cho \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c, t\u00f4i tin Selecao \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</em>.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-fairplay-gui-loi-chuc-chien-thang-den-ca-phap-va-croatia-421-191144.html\">Neymar g\u1eedi t\u00e2m th\u01b0 ch\u00fac chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-khien-huyen-thoai-brazil-that-vong-tran-tre-421-191030.html\">Neymar khi\u1ebfn huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/an-tuong-world-cup/dung-lac-loi-nua-hoi-cac-vu-cong-samba-471-190954.html\">B\u00e0i d\u1ef1 thi \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng World Cup: \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea1c l\u1ed1i n\u1eefa h\u1ee1i c\u00e1c v\u0169 c\u00f4ng Samba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/trao-luu-moi-dau-ruot-voi-thu-thach-neymar-tren-toan-the-gioi-421-190849.html\">Tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u m\u1edbi: \u0110au ru\u1ed9t v\u1edbi &ldquo;Th\u1eed th\u00e1ch Neymar&rdquo; tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/fernandinho-bi-doa-giet-vi-ban-phan-luoi-trong-tran-brazil-thua-bi-188-190755.html\">Fernandinho b\u1ecb d\u1ecda gi\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi trong tr\u1eadn Brazil thua B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1370","checkdouble":"191472"},{"date":"07:36 18/07","title":"M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: \u201cKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/me-ronaldo-khong-the-tro-lai-mu-la-dieu-dang-tiec.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u00e0 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Real Madrid. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn c\u00f9ng ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay sau 9 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u00e1nh m\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Manchester United. C\u0110V c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 M.U v\u00e0 Ronaldo hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 cu\u1ed9c t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed di\u1ec5n ra. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, CR7 t\u1eebng c\u00f3 6 n\u0103m ch\u01a1i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00f2ng c\u00e1c Manucians.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i MU nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/Cristiano-Ronaldo-khong-the-tro-lai-MU-nhu-du-dinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed1t cu\u1ed9c, M.U \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Juventus nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 99 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 112 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Maria Dolores Aveiro t\u1eebng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1ea5y anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man United. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y b\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n con trai m\u00ecnh khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Alexis Sanchez hay Romelu Lukaku trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ba Aveiro va Ronaldo\" title=\"ba Aveiro va Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/ba-Aveiro-va-Ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u00e0 Aveiro ti\u1ebfc khi Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00e0 Aveiro tin r\u1eb1ng Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn nh\u1ea5t cho m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Italia. &ldquo;Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee9ng ph\u00eda sau n\u00f3&rdquo;, Aveiro n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;S\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng Ronaldo k\u00fd v\u1edbi Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2022. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 CLB l\u1edbn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a CR7 b\u1edfi khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac giao k\u00e8o n\u00e0y, anh s\u1ebd 37 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/ronaldo-tiet-lo-soc-ve-vu-chuyen-nhuong-toi-juventus-184-191410.html\">Ronaldo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi Juventus</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/kaka-phat-bieu-ve-viec-ronaldo-toi-juventus-176-191405.html\">Ronaldo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus v\u1edbi Milan l\u00e0&hellip; \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-real-noi-gi-khi-ronaldo-toi-juventus-180-191404.html\">HLV Real n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/mourinho-ronaldo-se-phuc-hung-bong-da-y-176-191396.html\">Mourinho: &ldquo;Ronaldo s\u1ebd ph\u1ee5c h\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1369","checkdouble":"191474"},{"date":"07:56 18/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7: \u201cG\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng\u201d World Cup ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-187-gang-tay-vang-world-cup-tien-sat-toi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 18/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Boca Juniors mu\u1ed1n m\u01b0\u1ee3n &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Barca. </strong>Boca Juniors r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Colombia. G\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 Argentina m\u1edbi g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u01b0\u1ee3n 1 n\u0103m gi\u00e1 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t t\u1edbi Barcelona.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real Madrid. </strong>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 mua l\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111o\u1ea1t G\u0103ng tay v\u00e0ng World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 187 Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 187 Courtois ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t t\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/world-cup-2018-khep-lai-voi-nhung-danh-hieu-ca-nhan-xung-dang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Courtois</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Blind ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ajax. </strong>Man United x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Daley Blind \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ajax v\u1edbi h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 14 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng H\u00e0 Lan t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2014. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chia tay sau 4 n\u0103m, Blind c\u00f9ng M.U \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 1 c\u00fap FA, 1 c\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 Europa League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm cho Alisson.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Alisson khi \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd n\u1eb1m \u1edf cu\u1ed9c th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u00e0 AS Roma. Liverpool \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 72 tri\u1ec7u Euro (62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) cho Alisson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1edbt l\u1edd Bayern.</strong> Jordan Pickford m\u1edbi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi t\u1eeb g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 \u0110\u1ee9c, Bayern Munich \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, gi\u00fap \u0110TQG l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Pickford\" title=\"thu mon Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/David-Moyes-phat-bieu-ve-Jordan-Pickford-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Pickford t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Bayern \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>M\u1eb9 Ronaldo: &ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc&rdquo;.</strong> Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 v\u00e0 m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a CR7 c\u0169ng m\u1edbi x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>&ldquo;Brazil c\u1ee7a Tite v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i&rdquo;.</strong> Kaka ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Tite c\u00f2n c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c CSKA \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. </strong>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Evgeniy Giner, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CSKA Moscow x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1368","checkdouble":"191475"},{"date":"08:43 18/07","title":"HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 danh s\u00e1ch t\u1eadp trung \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/19/hlv-le-thuy-hai-noi-gi-ve-danh-sach-tap-trung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn khi ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua 17/7, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/vff-cong-bo-danh-sach-30-tuyen-thu-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191430.html\" target=\"_blank\">danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam </span>\u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. Trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 26 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i U23 v\u00e0 4 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean 23 g\u1ed3m \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng Park n\u00ean g\u1ecdi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 23 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam mat co hoi doi dau nguoi Uc\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1ea5t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dac\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/croatia-viet-tiep-cau-chuyen-20-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV L\u00ea Th\u1ee5y H\u1ea3i cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7n g\u1ecdi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng Olympic VN</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng cho hay: &quot;Theo t\u00f4i, HLV Park Hang Seo n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 sau v\u00f2ng 20, V.League 2018 xem th\u1eed c\u00f3 th\u00eam g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt hay kh\u00f4ng r\u1ed3i g\u1ecdi th\u00eam t\u1eeb 1 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i l\u00ean h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 th\u00e1ng n\u1eefa gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi di\u1ec5n ra, ch\u00fang ta c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu. \u0110\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n h\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng k\u00fd danh s\u00e1ch r\u1ed3i ch\u1ed1t 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed9n. L\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u00f4ng Park c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u00f4ng H\u1ea3i &ldquo;l\u01a1&rdquo; c\u0169ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng Park c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m, th\u00ec nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb CLB n\u00e0o, hay CLB th\u00ec 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi nh\u01b0ng CLB kh\u00e1c l\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1. G\u1ecdi ai v\u00e0 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. \u0110i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang ta quan t\u00e2m l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb nh\u01b0 n\u00e0o, ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n ra sao \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ASIAD v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cao nh\u1ea5t&rdquo;, HLV L\u00ea Thu\u1ef5 H\u1ea3i cho bi\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 25/7 t\u1edbi 3/9/2018. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ra 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ASIAD.</p>\r\n<h2>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ho\u00e0ng (S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (FLC Thanh H\u00f3a), \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7: Hu\u1ef3nh T\u1ea5n Sinh (Qu\u1ea3ng Nam FC), Ph\u1ea1m Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh (SLNA), Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh, Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u00e0nh Chung, \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), V\u0169 V\u0103n Thanh, L\u00ea V\u0103n S\u01a1n, Nguy\u1ec5n Phong H\u1ed3ng Duy (HAGL), B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng, Nguy\u1ec5n Tr\u1ecdng \u0110\u1ea1i (Viettel), Tr\u1ecbnh V\u0103n L\u1ee3i (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng)</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7: Ph\u1ea1m \u0110\u1ee9c Huy, Nguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Tri\u1ec7u Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (HAGL), L\u00ea Ph\u1ea1m Th\u00e0nh Long (H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng), Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c (SLNA)&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o: Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC), Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n To\u00e0n, Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (HAGL), Ho\u00e0ng Minh Tu\u1ea5n (Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh), H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh (SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng), Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh (B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng).&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/10/1/hang-thu-dtvn-can-lam-bong-dang-mot-nhu-thanh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-guong-mat-bi-hlv-park-hang-seo-bo-quen-tai-asiad-2018-168-191462.html\">Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo &lsquo;b\u1ecf qu\u00ean&rsquo; t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nL\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u00e9m duy\u00ean ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u1edf gi\u1ea3i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/29/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-bu-tottenham-canh-tranh-hcv-asiad-cung-lua-cong-phuong-168-191451.html\">Sao b\u1ef1 Tottenham c\u1ea1nh tranh HCV ASIAD c\u00f9ng l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nCh\u00e2n s\u00fat Tottenham v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c L\u0110B\u0110 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1n t\u00ean v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/22/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-tu-danh-sach-trieu-tap-dt-olympic-viet-nam-du-asiad-2018-168-191444.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec t\u1eeb danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\nChi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 17/7, danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1. V\u00e0 nh\u00ecn t\u1eeb b\u1ea3n danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y, ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</div>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1367","checkdouble":"191477"},{"date":"08:53 18/07","title":"HLV Croatia: \"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Barca\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/16/hlv-croatia-toi-co-the-dan-dat-brazil-hoac-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 Barca nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Croatia lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u01b0a th\u00edch.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dalic v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1edbn</span>. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D, b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Argentina. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 3-0.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Zlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/hlv-croatia-toi-co-the-dan-dat-brazil-hoac-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Croatia \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCroatia c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft d\u00f9 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Dalic \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u1eafng 2-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c l\u1ef1c \u1edf 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-4. D\u00f9 sao v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u00e1 qu\u00e2n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trong s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng v\u1ea1n NHM. HLV Dalic ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc caro. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i cho th\u1ea5y t\u00e0i n\u0103ng trong vi\u1ec7c truy\u1ec1n s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt hay nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Dalic n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, HLV Dalic l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Dalic mu\u1ed1n ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Guong mat duom buon cua HLV Dalic\" title=\"G\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3m bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/hlv.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0HLV Dalic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Brazil ho\u1eb7c Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZlatko Dalic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 51 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0110T Brazil v\u00e0 Barca nh\u01b0ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T Croatia lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c \u01b0a th\u00edch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Brazil ho\u1eb7c Barcelona, t\u00f4i tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cV\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i \u0111au khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn chung k\u1ebft. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1366","checkdouble":"191480"},{"date":"20:37 17/07","title":"Rami: \"Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/rami-pogba-da-tro-thanh-mot-nha-lanh-dao-thuc-su.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Adil Rami cho r\u1eb1ng Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o sau khi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Pogba t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pogba \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 anh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00e2ng cao v\u00e0 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Man United \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 minh ch\u1ee9ng cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Pogba. V\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh c\u1ea7n anh nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<h2>Rami ca ng\u1ee3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rami khen Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rami khen Pogba \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/rami-pogba-da-tro-thanh-mot-nha-lanh-dao-thuc-su.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba \u0111ang d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Pogba l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Moscow, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rami chia s\u1ebb: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng Paul Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00edch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt kh\u00f3 nh\u01b0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u00e2y gi\u1edd Pogba \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n trong kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng. L\u00fac n\u00e0y, Pogba \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1eabn l\u1ed1i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nPogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018. Man United hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i ICC. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Pogba:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-duoc-khuyen-nen-trao-bang-doi-truong-cho-pogba-172-191419.html\">Mourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean trao b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng cho Pogba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cac-huyen-thoai-mu-ca-ngoi-pogba-cho-phep-doi-kieu-toc-421-191349.html\">C\u00e1c huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, cho ph\u00e9p... \u0111\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3u t\u00f3c</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1365","checkdouble":"191460"},{"date":"20:55 17/07","title":"\"Ronaldo s\u1ebd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/ronaldo-se-hoi-han-voi-quyet-dinh-roi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Christian Panucci d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n Ronaldo s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Juventus nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc khi r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Real.</h2><h2>Panucci c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Panucci t\u1eebng gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga, Si\u00eau c\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Champions League v\u00e0 C\u00fap th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00e1c CLB trong 3 n\u0103m kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid. Sau \u0111\u00f3, anh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Inter nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 x\u01b0a. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed5 v\u1ee1 quan h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi HLV Marcelo Lippi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 45 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ronaldo th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Serie A. Nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng CR7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Real.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo r\u1eddi  Real, nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Panucci h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo r\u1eddi  Real, nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o t\u1eeb Panucci h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/ronaldo-se-hoi-han-voi-quyet-dinh-roi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Panucci c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Ronaldo s\u1ebd h\u1ed1i h\u1eadn khi r\u1eddi Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi t\u00f4i r\u1eddi Real, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 h\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00f3.</em></div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1edfi v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. N\u00f3i th\u1eb3ng ra th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00f4ng minh c\u1ee7a Juventus. S\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00f4i k\u00e9o nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Italia. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ADN c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Panucci d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian chuy\u1ec3n giao kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi HLV Zinedine <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/soc-zidane-bat-ngo-tu-chuc-hlv-real-madrid-180-187457.html\" target=\"_blank\">Zidane c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 chia tay s\u00e2n Bernabeu</span> v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi Julen Lopetegui.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nZidane \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng La Liga \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. V\u00e0 Panucci cho r\u1eb1ng Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 thay th\u1ebf ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Zidane \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i, Ronaldo c\u0169ng ra \u0111i. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf h\u1ecd v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Champions League\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-ve-tuong-lai-gareth-bale-180-191416.html\">Real Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Gareth Bale</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-phat-bieu-ve-real-180-191412.html\">V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV tai ti\u1ebfng t\u1ef1 tin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1364","checkdouble":"191461"},{"date":"20:48 17/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t b\u1ecb HLV Park Hang Seo \u2018b\u1ecf qu\u00ean\u2019 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2015/10/1/hang-thu-dtvn-can-lam-bong-dang-mot-nhu-thanh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi AS Roma \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi AS Roma. Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. The Kop nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin vui t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Roma r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm. Real t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32 trong khi Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm g\u1ea5p ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Thibaut Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/liverpool-muon-mua-alisson-gia-62-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNghe \u0111\u00e2u, Liverpool v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Roma, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c sau khi b\u00e1n Mohamed Salah cho ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRoma \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Liverpool l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1ea3 Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 75 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>The Kop r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00fac m\u1eafc gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin cho hay Liverpool v\u00e0 Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loris Karius doi dien tuong lai bat on sau man trinh dien te hai o chung ket Champions League.\" title=\"Loris Karius \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/Dan-anh-du-doan-Karius-tro-lai-manh-me-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Karius</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlphonse Areola c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain r\u1ed3i Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Roma. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Liverpool, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng Loris Karius, Simon Mignolet hay Danny Ward kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho c\u00e1c tham v\u1ecdng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o n\u00fat Like m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u00f3 hai n\u1eefa Roma v\u00e0 Liverpool chia \u0111\u00f4i. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y ng\u1ea7m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool-172-191445.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chi-160-trieu-euro-klopp-muon-mang-ve-liverpool-3-ngoi-sao-187-191414.html\">Chi 160 tri\u1ec7u euro, Klopp mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 Liverpool 3 ng\u00f4i sao</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-nguoi-bi-quen-lang-172-191409.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-duoc-mo-duong-chieu-mo-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-191370.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff-172-191368.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1363","checkdouble":"191462"},{"date":"22:45 17/07","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea khuy\u00ean Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hazard-can-phai-chuyen-den-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Craig Burley cho r\u1eb1ng Hazard c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i theo g\u01b0\u01a1ng Ronaldo, t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Premier League v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Burley khuy\u00ean Hazard r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eden <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real-172-191169.html\" target=\"_blank\">Hazard \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Real</span> Madrid \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. V\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c h\u01a1n trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Craig Burley c\u1ee7a Chelsea cho r\u1eb1ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real. B\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Chelsea khuy\u00ean Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Chelsea khuy\u00ean Hazard \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hazard-can-phai-chuyen-den-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Burley cho r\u1eb1ng Hazard c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cHazard \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 6 n\u0103m. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f3. Nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111ang b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Chelsea. Sarri l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid khi h\u1ecd ng\u1ecf l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng? V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi Ronaldo r\u1eddi Man United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n nh\u1eb1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac Hazard \u0111i l\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p m\u1edbi\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Hazard \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hazard v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Chelsea sau khi \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh t\u1edbi 6 n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Anh. G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i Chelsea l\u00e0 ph\u00eda n\u1eafm quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cSau 6 n\u0103m tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Chelsea, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i khai ph\u00e1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, sau k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf. Nh\u01b0ng Chelsea l\u00e0 b\u00ean n\u1eafm quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jorginho-chia-khoa-thanh-cong-cua-sarri-172-191455.html\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho: Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Sarri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191438.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1362","checkdouble":"191463"},{"date":"01:14 18/07","title":"\"\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Euro 2020\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/dt-anh-da-bi-bat-bai-va-kho-canh-tranh-o-euro-2020.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Merson cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf Euro 2020.</h2><h2>\u0110T Anh g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ecdi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. V\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c C\u0110V Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Croatia lo\u1ea1i \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thua c\u1ea3 B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh h\u1ea1ng ba.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Merson e ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Anh t\u1ea1i Euro 2020\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Euro 2020 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf Euro 2020 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/dt-anh-da-bi-bat-bai-va-kho-canh-tranh-o-euro-2020.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Merson \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro 2020</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Paul Merson cho r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 t\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh. C\u0169ng v\u00ec v\u1eady m\u00e0 Merson cho r\u1eb1ng Tam S\u01b0 kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf Euro 2020 sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ecb s\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Euro sau \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 World Cup khi t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 h\u1ecd thua c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tranh h\u1ea1ng ba. B\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng th\u1ebf. B\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn\u00a0 \u1edf k\u1ef3 Euro t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ch\u00fang ta.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng quang \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKieran Trippier \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. Harry Maguire c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 g\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng n\u00ean ch\u00fat t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc l\u00e0 Pickford. M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m t\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng ngo\u00e0i 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f3 ra th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ai n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ea3\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mourinho-che-sterling-khong-du-trinh-da-chinh-o-dt-anh-421-191257.html\">Mourinho ch\u00ea Sterling kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-bong-da-dang-tro-lai-voi-rieng-nguoi-xu-angle-465-191221.html\">\u0110T Anh: B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi ri\u00eang x\u1ee9 \u0102ng-l\u00ea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1361","checkdouble":"191464"},{"date":"05:39 18/07","title":"Quy\u1ebft c\u00f3 Alisson, Liverpool chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/6/liverpool-muon-mua-alisson-gia-62-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi AS Roma \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Real Madrid v\u00e0 Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool t\u00ednh t\u1ea1o \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi AS Roma. Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y. The Kop nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin vui t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Roma r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh l\u1edbn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u00e0 Chelsea trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Liverpool chi \u0111\u1eadm. Real t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m thay th\u1ebf Keylor Navas chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32 trong khi Chelsea c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm g\u1ea5p ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Thibaut Courtois ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 r\u1ee5c r\u1ecbch ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/liverpool-muon-mua-alisson-gia-62-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 62 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNghe \u0111\u00e2u, Liverpool v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alisson v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u1edf ng\u1ea1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd l\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Roma, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c sau khi b\u00e1n Mohamed Salah cho ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRoma \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i r\u00f5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Liverpool l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u00e1i di\u1ec5n. H\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1ea3 Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 75 tri\u1ec7u Euro).<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>The Kop r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00fac m\u1eafc gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Gi\u1edbi th\u1ea1o tin cho hay Liverpool v\u00e0 Roma c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Loris Karius doi dien tuong lai bat on sau man trinh dien te hai o chung ket Champions League.\" title=\"Loris Karius \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf chung k\u1ebft Champions League.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/5/Dan-anh-du-doan-Karius-tro-lai-manh-me-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o Karius</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlphonse Areola c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain r\u1ed3i Gianluigi Donnarumma c\u1ee7a AC Milan \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Roma. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Liverpool, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng Loris Karius, Simon Mignolet hay Danny Ward kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u1ee7 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn vai tr\u00f2 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho c\u00e1c tham v\u1ecdng m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Alisson m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o n\u00fat Like m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u00f3 hai n\u1eefa Roma v\u00e0 Liverpool chia \u0111\u00f4i. \u0110\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i n\u00e0y ng\u1ea7m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 25 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 xa.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-khi-xherdan-shaqiri-cap-ben-liverpool-172-191445.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi Xherdan Shaqiri c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/chi-160-trieu-euro-klopp-muon-mang-ve-liverpool-3-ngoi-sao-187-191414.html\">Chi 160 tri\u1ec7u euro, Klopp mu\u1ed1n mang v\u1ec1 Liverpool 3 ng\u00f4i sao</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-chia-se-dieu-bat-ngo-ve-nguoi-bi-quen-lang-172-191409.html\">Klopp chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb qu\u00ean l\u00e3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-duoc-mo-duong-chieu-mo-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-172-191370.html\">Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/grujic-roi-liverpool-sang-cardiff-172-191368.html\">Sao tr\u1ebb Liverpool ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1360","checkdouble":"191465"},{"date":"06:00 18/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ch\u1ec9 ra b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/robert-pires-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal. C\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u1eebng danh m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00e2n binh s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 HLV Unai Emery.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng su\u00f4n s\u1ebb</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng vi\u00ean g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean x\u00e2y n\u00ean tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 5 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m Bernd Leno, Sokratis Papastathopoulos, Stephan Lichsteiner, Lucas Torreira v\u00e0 Matteo Guendouzi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a Arsenal nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Emery c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam 1, 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 l\u1edbn n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5y th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Robert Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Robert-Pires-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sokratis l\u00e0 1 trong 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Arsenal t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00f3 tin Arsenal t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kingsley Coman c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 44 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hai b\u00ean c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh s\u1ed1 1</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nQu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb. Song trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ef1u Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 Robert Pires l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u201cB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Unai Emery, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng\u201d, anh n\u00f3i v\u1edbi Sky Sports.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/robert-pires-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pires ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng Emery l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean, t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Emery, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t CLB l\u1edbn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cEmery \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u1ecb HLV n\u00e0y s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Arsenal.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00e0y 12/8 t\u1edbi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Premier League b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Man City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 1 tu\u1ea7n sau, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-emery-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-172-191065.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-so-huu-tan-binh-thu-5-172-190980.html\">N\u00d3NG: Arsenal ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 5</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chinh-thuc-xac-nhan-co-tan-binh-thu-4-tri-gia-30-trieu-euro-172-190886.html\">Arsenal CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 4 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes-172-190877.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wenger-bat-bai-khoi-arsenal-vikante-172-190866.html\">Wenger b\u1eadt b\u00e3i kh\u1ecfi Arsenal v\u00ec...Kante?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1359","checkdouble":"191466"},{"date":"06:19 18/07","title":"Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/15/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia nh\u1eafm ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5p v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 Andres Iniesta \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEden Hazard m\u1edbi c\u00f3 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T B\u1ec9. Ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y l\u00e0 linh h\u1ed3n trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf, c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd gi\u00e0nh h\u1ea1ng 3 t\u1ea1i ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng ngay sau khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, Hazard l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Chelsea bu\u1ed3n l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3, gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00f4i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t\u201d, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean h\u1ebft t\u00f4i v\u1eabn d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i t\u1eeb h\u1ecd.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/15/023624-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hazard t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Antonio Conte c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi Hazard. Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Maurizio Sarri v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u00e0nh cho Hazard v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Real Madrid sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao kh\u00e1c thay th\u1ebf. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Barcelona. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 Andres Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p th\u1eadt \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard vo dich FA Cup\" title=\"Eden Hazard vo dich FA Cup\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/chelsea-chi-100-trieu-bang-de-giu-chan-hazard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Don Balon \u0111\u01b0a tin Barca c\u1ea1nh tranh Hazard v\u1edbi Real. Vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng g\u1ed3m Hazard, Coutinho, Messi v\u00e0 Suarez v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n 200 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u1edbi ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea3 Hazard. L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Barca bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p \u0111\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 cho Chelsea s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t 120 tri\u1ec7u Euro c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam sao tr\u1ebb Ousmane Dembele \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Hazard. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Barca t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 155 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Dembele t\u1eeb Borussia Dormund. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng b\u1ecf r\u1ebb tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng quang World Cup 2018 cho Chelsea v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 t\u00ednh ra ch\u1ec9 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 nh\u00fan nh\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/andre-gomes-muon-toi-tottenham-172-191411.html\">Sao th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Barca mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Harry Kane t\u1ea1i Premier League</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/he-lo-2-tan-binh-tiep-theo-se-duoc-barca-cong-bo-trong-tuan-toi-187-191356.html\">H\u00e9 l\u1ed9 2 t\u00e2n binh ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-vuot-mat-arsenal-vu-tien-ve-nzonzi-180-191340.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Arsenal v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-hung-croatia-danh-tieng-cho-real-madrid-va-barcelona-421-191189.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Croatia \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chan-mu-pogba-co-dong-thai-san-sang-dau-quan-cho-barca-172-191187.html\">Ch\u00e1n M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1358","checkdouble":"191467"},{"date":"06:42 18/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c CSKA \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Evgeniy Giner, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CSKA Moscow x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea nh\u1eafm Golovin</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAleksandr Golovin m\u1edbi tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 kh\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng \u0110T Nga. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 \u201cl\u00e1 ph\u1ed5i\u201d n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 b\u1ea1ch d\u01b0\u01a1ng, ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao. D\u00f9 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, \u0111i b\u00f3ng hay tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, Golovin \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c ra Golovin \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng t\u1eeb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 t\u1ea1i CSKA. Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/20180614T165656Z_486856268_RC1444D35830_RTRMADP_3_SOCCERWORLDCUPRUSSAU.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd sau World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau Arsenal, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin. V\u00e0 khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau n\u00e0y b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh Lucas Torreira, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a The Blues c\u00e0ng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin h\u00f4m qua r\u1eb1ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Golovin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>CSKA ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e1n Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Evgeniy Giner c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nga cho bi\u1ebft b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Golovin s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh r\u1ed3i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>CSKA ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n Golovin cho Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng phung ph\u00ed t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 Golovin ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng ngay ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft\u201d, Giner n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u1edd Sport24 c\u1ee7a Nga. \u201cKhi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f4ng khai.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt v\u1eady, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Monaco (Vadim Vasilyev) gh\u00e9 th\u0103m v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb cho Golovin. C\u00f2n Chelsea? Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 CLB m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Golovin s\u1ebd s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129, ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Golovin xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Nga. Anh \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-quyet-dau-voi-real-vi-eden-hazard-180-191467.html\">Barca quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Real v\u00ec Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/courtois-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-tai-chelsea-172-191438.html\">Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Chelsea ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ben-do-moi-cua-morata-neu-roi-chelsea-172-191433.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Morata n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muon-thanh-cong-hlv-sarri-can-phai-ban-eden-hazard-172-191432.html\">Mu\u1ed1n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, HLV Sarri c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n Eden Hazard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-115-trieu-bang-cho-ng